Class: 'Allergic process (qualifier value)'

Annotations (3)

  • rdfs:label "Allergic process (qualifier value)" @en
  • skos:definition "A type of immune mediated hypersensitivity process that represents the underlying mechanism of allergic conditions." @en
  • skos:prefLabel "Allergic process" @en

Superclasses (1)
